{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/2024-06-22-how-to-add-glowing-text-in-react-js/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To aHoisting! To add glowing text in react js, you can use . It will add glowing text in react js. Today, I am going to show you, how to‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aHoisting!</p>\n<p>To add glowing text in react js, you can use <code class=\"language-text\">animation: glow 1.5s infinite alternate;</code>. It will add glowing text in react js.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, how to add glowing text in react js.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install and create a new React app.</li>\n<li>Import react component.</li>\n<li>Create a Component.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let‚Äôs start with the first step.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Install and create a new React app.</h3>\n<p>First you have to install the React project. You should use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> command to create a new React project.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npx create<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\ncd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 2: Import react component.</h3>\n<p>After installing, you have to import your React component. To do this, add the following line to the top of your component file.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./App.css'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 3: Create a Component.</h3>\n<p>You can use <code class=\"language-text\">className=\"glowing-text-dynamic\"</code> to add glowing text in react js.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"glowing-text-dynamic\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n   aHoisting Dynamic Glowing Text\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Define the add glowing text example.</h3>\n<p>The below code is an example of a React. You have to import <code class=\"language-text\">./App.css</code> and set <code class=\"language-text\">animation: glow 1.5s infinite alternate;</code> to add glowing text in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./App.css'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"glowing-text-dynamic\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    aHoisting Dynamic Glowing Text\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.css</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.glowing-text-dynamic</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2rem<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 0 5px #0ff<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0 0 10px #0ff<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0 0 20px #0ff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> glow 1.5s infinite alternate<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@keyframes</span> glow</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">from</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">text-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 0 5px #0ff<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0 0 10px #0ff<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0 0 20px #0ff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">to</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">text-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 0 10px #0ff<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0 0 20px #0ff<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0 0 40px #0ff<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0 0 80px #0ff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">@keyframes glow</code> and add glowing text in react js.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3ef158721b5553d00e25fe900c1170c9/59680/glowing-text.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.177215189873415%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRlIAAABXRUJQVlA4IEYAAACwAwCdASoUAAcAPtFcpkyoJSOiMAgBABoJYwCdH8ADA1m3QxEqAAD+sj+/1IQHQ4fNt2seV0NqmeN0dA3hzUIa5+Ai4AAA'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, add, glowing, text\"\n        title=\"React, add, glowing, text\"\n        src=\"/static/3ef158721b5553d00e25fe900c1170c9/8aab1/glowing-text.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3ef158721b5553d00e25fe900c1170c9/81b7c/glowing-text.webp 158w,\n/static/3ef158721b5553d00e25fe900c1170c9/6ea66/glowing-text.webp 315w,\n/static/3ef158721b5553d00e25fe900c1170c9/8aab1/glowing-text.webp 630w,\n/static/3ef158721b5553d00e25fe900c1170c9/59680/glowing-text.webp 632w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to add glowing text in react js?","tags":["React"],"date":"June 22, 2024","description":"Example of add glowing text in react js with step by step tutorial - aHoisting","social_image":{"absolutePath":"/Users/mac/Documents/hoisting/ahoisting/static/media/template/reactjs.jpg"}}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to add greater than symbol in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2024-06-23-how-to-add-greater-than-symbol-in-react-js/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to add google map in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2024-06-12-how-to-add-google-map-in-react-js/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2024-06-22-how-to-add-glowing-text-in-react-js/","prevSlug":"/blog/2024-06-23-how-to-add-greater-than-symbol-in-react-js/","nextSlug":"/blog/2024-06-12-how-to-add-google-map-in-react-js/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2555585279","2714594843","3159585216"]}